            a(href='../../2012/noh-theatre-plus-experiment-black-milk-impulses/') Noh Plus – Noh theatre experiment with Black Milk Impulses
          time(pubdate) August 28, 2012
        p Improvisations to Noh theatre with intermittent original sound.
        p
          a(href='http://gianpaolocamplese.it/' title='Gianpaolo Camplese' target='_blank') Gianpaolo Camplese
          |  – drums
          br
          | Leo Auri – laptop
        p Our five minute trailer version for the uninitiated:
        .embed-container
          iframe(src='https://player.vimeo.com/video/67651461' frameborder='0' webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen).
            
            
        p
          | And for dedicated fans and Noh nuts, treat yourself to the full version via 
          a(href='https://vimeo.com/album/2148348' title='Noh Plus (Black Milk Impulses) on Vimeo' target='_blank') vimeo
          | .
