        p I wrote and produced music for The Call, a play written by Peter Scollin, directed by Anja Scollin, played by Amy Nye, Ben Maddox and Oskar Brown, and premiering on the 9th December, 2011. I’ve now converted it into an “album” and released it over Bandcamp:
        p
